It’s all piled high on our fresh-baked Italian Herbs and Cheese bread.'}, {'menu_id': 6, 'item': 'The Sliced Avocado Spike Bowl by Gronk', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, and green peppers piled high with shredded Monterey cheddar, a helping of sliced avocado and topped with our Baja Chipotle Sauce for a smoky kick that will bowl you over.'}, {'menu_id': 7, 'item': 'The Avocado Spike Bowl by Gronk', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, and green peppers piled high with shredded Monterey cheddar, a helping of smashed avocado and topped with our Baja Chipotle Sauce for a smoky kick that will bowl you over.'}], 'Classic Sandwiches': [{'menu_id': 1, 'item': 'Cold Cut Combo®', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': "The Cold Cut Combo® sandwich with ham, salami, and bologna (all turkey based) is a long-time Subway® favorite. JSON:
{'Subway 10134-0 Menu en-US': {'No Bready Bowls™': [{'menu_id': 1, 'item': 'B.L.T.', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'The classic B.L.T., in a bowl. It’s that simple. But of course, you can add your favorite veggies, too.'}, {'menu_id': 2, 'item': 'Rotisserie-Style Chicken', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Fuel up with juicy rotisserie-style chicken, piled high on whatever veggies you happen to be in the mood for.'}, {'menu_id': 3, 'item': 'Roast Beef', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'A generous portion of Choice Angus Roast Beef and veggies: this is a Protein Bowl that packs a punch.'}, {'menu_id': 4, 'item': 'Oven Roasted Turkey & Ham', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Our thin-sliced, oven roasted turkey and Black Forest ham make an unbeatable duo, especially sitting on top of all your favorite veggies.'}, {'menu_id': 5, 'item': 'Meatball Marinara', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'When it comes to the Meatball Marinara Protein Bowl, we won’t skimp on the protein. You’ll get spinach, peppers and other veggies plus all eight meatballs (count ‘em!) you’d find on a Footlong.'}, {'menu_id': 6, 'item': 'Buffalo Chicken', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': "Packed with grilled chicken, plus just the right amount of Frank's RedHot® Buffalo sauce, a little peppercorn ranch to beat the heat and all the veggies you can fit in there. Frank’s RedHot® is a registered trademark of McCormick & Co. and used under license by Subway Franchisee Advertising Fund Trust Ltd. ®/© Subway IP LLC 2021."}, {'menu_id': 7, 'item': 'Spicy Italian', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'How do you turn your go-to Spicy Italian into a powerful Protein Bowl? You take all of the pepperoni and Genoa salami (seriously, every last slice!) you’d find on a Footlong and add it to a bowl with your pick of veggies.'}, {'menu_id': 8, 'item': 'Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'The amazing Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki protein bowl carries its weight in deliciousness. It starts light with a veggie delight of lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers, black olives, and red onions, but then here come the big, heavy hitters—the juicy, grilled chicken strips topped with our Sweet Onion Teriyaki sauce. It’s all that, and more.'}, {'menu_id': 9, 'item': 'Pizza Sub', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'We made pizza into a sub, then made that into a bowl. Why not? Packed with pepperoni, Monterey cheddar cheese and topped with marinara sauce. Feel free to add all the fresh veggies you (and the bowl) can handle.'}, {'menu_id': 10, 'item': 'Italian B.M.T.®', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Big. Meaty. Tasty. And we mean meaty. You’ll get all the salami, pepperoni and ham you’d find on a Footlong Italian B.M.T®. on top of shredded lettuce, tomatoes, cucumbers and more. Yeah, that works.'}, {'menu_id': 11, 'item': 'Oven Roasted Turkey', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Get all the flavor you’d find in an Oven Roasted Turkey Footlong, without sacrificing an ounce of protein. The Oven Roasted Turkey Protein Bowl is loaded with your choice of veggies and topped with all the thin-sliced turkey you’d get in your favorite Footlong.'}, {'menu_id': 12, 'item': 'Chicken & Bacon Ranch', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Fuel your day with every last bite of Rotisserie-Style Chicken, Monterrey Cheddar Cheese, and Hickory-Smoked Bacon you’d get in a Footlong, now in a bowl with veggies and Peppercorn Ranch.'}, {'menu_id': 13, 'item': 'Tuna', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'How much tuna? A Footlong’s worth of tuna, that’s how much. Enjoy your go-to protein, 100% wild caught tuna, mixed with mayo on top of a bed of fresh lettuce with your choice of veggies. That’s a tuna Protein Bowl.'}, {'menu_id': 14, 'item': 'Steak & Cheese', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'Packed with protein and stacked with veggies, the Steak & Cheese Protein Bowl is everything you love about your favorite Footlong — literally, it has the same amount of juicy steak — plus peppers, onions and more.'}, {'menu_id': 15, 'item': 'Black Forest Ham', 'item-price': '', 'item-description': 'A Footlong’s worth of protein? Yup!
